lead_paragraph: Chicago Cubs infielder Kris Bryant and pitchers Jon Lester and Kyle Hendricks have the chance to add more hardware to their magical season after Major League Baseball announced them as finalists for the league’s top awards.

headline.print_headline: Bryant and Cubs Team Mates Up for Major Awards
